Reasoning: The paper deals with the problem of Pose Graph Optimization, which is a fundamental problem in robotics and computer vision. The paper proposes a new approach based on Lagrangian duality and complex domain analysis to compute globally optimal solutions for PGO. This makes the paper relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), signal processing (cs.SI), and control systems (cs.SY).
